OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776334011
OL,3,CMan dies following collision between
OL,4,Ccar and bike on the Isle of Man
OL,6,FThe Isle of Man Constabulary say an
OL,7,Finvestigation into the circumstances
OL,8,Fsurrounding the collision is currently
OL,9,Funderway, and a male is currently
OL,10,Fassisting police with enquiries.
OL,12,FPolice are asking that the public
OL,13,F"refrain from speculation" and
OL,14,F"respect the family's privacy during
OL,15,Fthis difficult time".
